4
00:01:52,020 --> 00:01:53,640
This is the place.

5
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:57,350
It's so well hidden.

6
00:01:57,350 --> 00:02:00,950
After more than ten years, you still found it.

7
00:02:00,950 --> 00:02:04,400
Have you forgotten everything my father taught you about geomancy?

8
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:07,130
I never really learned properly.

9
00:02:09,980 --> 00:02:13,560
Right beneath our feet is the tunnel my father

10
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:15,780
used to take me then.

11
00:02:15,780 --> 00:02:21,640
It connects directly to the tomb passage, which is closest to the diamond wall.

12
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:26,030
When I left, my father told me to fill it up again,

13
00:02:26,030 --> 00:02:28,420
to keep tomb robbers out.

14
00:02:29,140 --> 00:02:33,090
If it's sealed off, how did Master get inside?

15
00:02:33,090 --> 00:02:34,860
My father was away in Dongxia for so long.

16
00:02:34,860 --> 00:02:38,370
Other tomb robbers must've discovered this place.

17
00:02:38,370 --> 00:02:41,250
Here's what we'll do: Split up and search.

18
00:03:24,490 --> 00:03:26,820
Guan Feng! Come here.

19
00:03:28,740 --> 00:03:30,220
Here.

20
00:03:56,750 --> 00:04:00,300
 Father, this tomb is actually for a married couple. 

21
00:04:00,300 --> 00:04:04,510
 Check around and find out who they were. 

22
00:04:25,140 --> 00:04:27,260
 The coffin decorations are exquisite, 

23
00:04:27,260 --> 00:04:29,340
 and the materials are high quality. 

24
00:04:29,340 --> 00:04:32,000
 This isn't an ordinary family's coffin. 

25
00:04:50,620 --> 00:04:52,930
 But why isn't there an inscription? 

26
00:05:05,460 --> 00:05:07,680
 This tomb owner is so strange. 

27
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:11,130
 The gold, jade, and coffin here are all top-quality, 

28
00:05:11,130 --> 00:05:12,940
 but there's no inscription. 

29
00:05:12,940 --> 00:05:18,000
 Could it be they didn't want their identity known? 

30
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:26,000
 Both sides of the coffin are full of books. 

31
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:31,420
 The owner was clearly a civil official, and a very high-ranking one at that. 

32
00:05:31,420 --> 00:05:35,340
 What kind of high official would need to hide their identity? 

33
00:05:40,410 --> 00:05:44,510
 I suspect the inscription is hidden inside this stone turtle. 

34
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:48,870
 Then why didn't he carve it openly on the outside, 

35
00:05:48,870 --> 00:05:51,430
 but hid it instead, where no one would find it? 

36
00:05:51,430 --> 00:05:55,110
 When Mom taught me, she mentioned a person who traveled everywhere, 

37
00:05:55,110 --> 00:05:57,530
 using money to stir conflict among nations. 

38
00:05:57,530 --> 00:06:00,310
 And if that didn't work, he'd assassinate them. 

39
00:06:00,310 --> 00:06:02,210
 That man was Liu Xian, the former Senior Secretary. 

40
00:06:02,210 --> 00:06:04,390
 He was used to hiding his true identity, 

41
00:06:04,390 --> 00:06:07,190
 so naturally, he'd hide his inscription, too. 

42
00:06:07,190 --> 00:06:10,070
 Let me check if it's really him. 

43
00:06:25,820 --> 00:06:26,920
 It really is Liu Xian! 

44
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:29,390
 It's really Liu Xian's tomb! 
   

45
00:06:29,390 --> 00:06:30,920
 Master. 

46
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:33,510
 We've finished checking Liu Xian's tomb tunnels. 

47
00:06:33,510 --> 00:06:36,390
 It seems like they've been digging for several days. 

48
00:06:36,390 --> 00:06:39,300
 They'll probably break through to the rear chamber in less than two days. 

49
00:06:39,300 --> 00:06:41,660
 And the tunnel we used to get in is connected to the passage. 

50
00:06:41,660 --> 00:06:43,290
 Luckily, the robbers died in the traps. 

51
00:06:43,290 --> 00:06:45,700
 Otherwise, this place would be ruined. 

52
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:48,480
 They'll definitely keep digging. 

53
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:51,750
 Wait here and catch them all. 

54
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:56,120
 And don't forget to fill up every single tunnel. 

55
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:58,680
 Nothing here should be disturbed. 

56
00:06:58,680 --> 00:06:59,720
 Yes. 

57
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,770
 The Imperial Astronomers are responsible 

58
00:07:01,770 --> 00:07:04,000
 for restoring and protecting important tombs, 

59
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:06,390
 but we're forbidden from excavating on our own. 

60
00:07:06,390 --> 00:07:07,900
 Understood. 

61
00:07:19,850 --> 00:07:21,810
There are burned torches on the ground.

62
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:30,400
Here.

63
00:07:58,380 --> 00:08:00,360
All cleaned out by tomb robbers.

64
00:08:01,090 --> 00:08:05,000
Judging from the tunnels, three groups of robbers came here.

65
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:08,880
Some died in traps,

66
00:08:10,460 --> 00:08:14,140
others died fighting each other.

67
00:08:17,700 --> 00:08:22,680
Then could what we're looking for already be gone?

68
00:08:24,020 --> 00:08:25,580
Split up and check around.

69
00:08:25,580 --> 00:08:28,700
If you find anything strange, tell me immediately.

70
00:08:28,700 --> 00:08:30,220
All right.

71
00:08:43,650 --> 00:08:45,220
Be careful!

72
00:08:45,670 --> 00:08:47,080
What's this thing?

73
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,680
Don't worry.

74
00:08:49,260 --> 00:08:51,320
This is Liu Xian's inscription.

75
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:16,320
The coffin is empty.

76
00:09:21,340 --> 00:09:23,770
Shi Lei, give me a hand.

77
00:09:24,770 --> 00:09:26,340
What are you doing?

78
00:09:26,340 --> 00:09:28,980
My father always said Imperial Astronomers

79
00:09:28,980 --> 00:09:31,430
must show respect for every person's remains.

80
00:09:31,430 --> 00:09:34,190
Even if we don't find what we're looking for,

81
00:09:34,190 --> 00:09:36,620
we should still give them a proper burial.

82
00:09:36,620 --> 00:09:40,140
Before we leave, restore the coffin to how it was.

83
00:09:43,460 --> 00:09:45,770
Why is this pattern reversed?

84
00:10:21,580 --> 00:10:24,896
   

85
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:29,030
Not even tomb robbers realized

86
00:10:29,030 --> 00:10:31,820
there's another secret hidden in Liu Xian's tomb.

87
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:46,270
This carving knife was my father's favorite.

88
00:10:46,270 --> 00:10:49,450
The handle of the knife has a chipped corner.

89
00:10:49,450 --> 00:10:51,800
My father felt bad about it for a long time.

90
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:58,460
It seems this carving was secretly made by my father.

91
00:11:02,860 --> 00:11:06,290
But if Master carved this,

92
00:11:06,290 --> 00:11:09,200
why did he leave one character blank at the end?

93
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:20,570
"The way of the sage can be summed up in one word..."

94
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:23,170
"Human"?

95
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,930
Or...

96
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:29,560
"Victory"?

97
00:11:31,020 --> 00:11:32,930
- Hey, stop! 
 - What's wrong?

98
00:11:32,930 --> 00:11:38,900
There are so many scattered characters here, but he left only one blank.

99
00:11:39,510 --> 00:11:42,520
I'm afraid that if we choose wrong, we won't get another chance.

100
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:44,950
Then, which character should we choose?

101
00:11:46,900 --> 00:11:51,960
A word that can summarize Shan Yi Zi's entire life...

102
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,570
Shan Yi Zi?

103
00:11:53,570 --> 00:11:56,320
Not Liu Xian?

104
00:11:57,220 --> 00:12:00,120
Look carefully at this carving.

105
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:04,690
It describes a sage who cared deeply for the people.

106
00:12:04,690 --> 00:12:08,690
These words couldn't describe Liu Xian.

107
00:12:08,690 --> 00:12:11,960
They can only refer to his master, Shan Yi Zi.

108
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:15,350
Liu Xian wasn't capable of traveling to many states

109
00:12:15,350 --> 00:12:17,510
and preserving peace, like Shan Yi Zi.

110
00:12:17,510 --> 00:12:21,920
All Liu Xian could do was create conflicts through schemes and assassinations,

111
00:12:21,920 --> 00:12:25,610
seeking his own benefit.

112
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:33,150
The thing he never understood is precisely this missing character.

113
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:52,530
"Virtue."

114
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:59,130
"Benevolence."

115
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:02,310
"Mercy."

116
00:13:03,030 --> 00:13:05,080
"Harmony."

117
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:19,690
"Balance."

118
00:13:22,510 --> 00:13:27,460
"The sage's way in one word is..."

119
00:13:32,290 --> 00:13:37,610
   

120
00:13:50,190 --> 00:13:54,010
Zhinu, is this the thing Master hid?

121
00:13:54,010 --> 00:13:56,270
The one they fought over,

122
00:13:56,270 --> 00:13:59,920
the thing that led them to destroy my entire family,

123
00:13:59,920 --> 00:14:01,750
is it this?

124
00:14:01,750 --> 00:14:04,160
Quick, take it out and see!

125
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:08,470
Shi Lei.

126
00:14:13,550 --> 00:14:15,300
Be careful!

127
00:14:57,380 --> 00:15:00,070
What... What is this thing?

128
00:15:00,710 --> 00:15:03,430
This isn't what we were looking for.

129
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:09,230
This is a bronze tube my father made.

130
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:15,440
 Father, didn't you always want to make this? 

131
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:18,410
 Now that it's finished, why aren't you happy? 

132
00:15:18,410 --> 00:15:22,440
 This bronze tube holds our ancestors' wisdom. 

133
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:26,270
 I studied ancient texts to find out how to make it. 

134
00:15:26,270 --> 00:15:28,440
 But when it was finally completed, 

135
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:30,560
 I suddenly realized 

136
00:15:30,560 --> 00:15:33,870
 I was too focused on its clever mechanisms 

137
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:38,850
 and overlooked that it's actually a weapon. 

138
00:15:38,850 --> 00:15:41,870
 If it falls into the wrong hands, 

139
00:15:41,870 --> 00:15:44,200
 the consequences could be disastrous. 

140
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:48,970
 Then let's hide it so no bad guys can find it. 

141
00:15:53,150 --> 00:15:55,380
 Zhinu, you're very clever. 

142
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:58,870
 All right. We'll put it away for now 

143
00:15:58,870 --> 00:16:03,900
 and find a place where no one will discover it. 

144
00:16:03,900 --> 00:16:07,320
After that, I never saw this bronze tube again.

145
00:16:07,320 --> 00:16:10,200
Only today did I realize

146
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:14,030
my father had hidden it here long ago.

147
00:16:14,030 --> 00:16:18,380
Was it the day he returned from Dongxia?

148
00:16:18,380 --> 00:16:20,200
No.

149
00:16:20,200 --> 00:16:23,900
It must have been when I was young, the time he brought me here.

150
00:16:23,900 --> 00:16:27,840
But if Master didn't visit here that day,

151
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:31,500
why did he take a detour home from the southwest?

152
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:36,290
Anyway, since Father didn't take the bronze tube,

153
00:16:36,290 --> 00:16:42,760
the thing he brought from Dongxia won't be here either.

154
00:16:42,760 --> 00:16:46,990
Let's go back. No need to search here anymore.

155
00:16:47,640 --> 00:16:49,780
Let's go.

156
00:17:06,830 --> 00:17:11,410
Zhinu, we didn't find the thing you're looking for.

157
00:17:11,410 --> 00:17:14,130
What should we do next?

158
00:17:14,130 --> 00:17:16,590
We didn't come away empty-handed.

159
00:17:16,590 --> 00:17:19,540
This bronze tube is extremely powerful.

160
00:17:19,540 --> 00:17:21,020
Compared to poisoning someone directly,

161
00:17:21,020 --> 00:17:24,530
this tube gives us better chances to succeed.

162
00:17:24,530 --> 00:17:26,070
Then let's kill him together.

163
00:17:26,070 --> 00:17:28,320
I... I can help you.

164
00:17:29,210 --> 00:17:33,870
No. We've only just reunited, and you're my only family now.

165
00:17:33,870 --> 00:17:36,670
I can't let you risk your life with me.

166
00:17:37,790 --> 00:17:40,770
But I can't let you go alone on such a dangerous mission!

167
00:17:40,770 --> 00:17:43,550
Guan Feng, trust me.

168
00:17:43,550 --> 00:17:46,950
I've already made a plan to escape safely.

169
00:17:46,950 --> 00:17:48,860
Are you sure?

170
00:17:51,310 --> 00:17:55,580
Once I'm done, we'll leave together.

171
00:17:55,580 --> 00:18:01,250
We'll find a beautiful place, where no one knows us.

172
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:09,350
Zhinu.

173
00:18:10,030 --> 00:18:12,990
You've always been smarter than me.

174
00:18:12,990 --> 00:18:14,690
Your plan must be a good one.

175
00:18:14,690 --> 00:18:19,440
But you must promise me to come back safely.

176
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:24,540
Don't worry. There's one more thing for you two.

177
00:18:24,540 --> 00:18:29,140
Fill up this tunnel and pack it tight.

178
00:18:32,790 --> 00:18:34,520
See you.

179
00:19:00,595 --> 00:19:04,300
   

180
00:19:04,300 --> 00:19:09,750
Sir, please deliver this letter to the gentleman in your storeroom.

181
00:19:09,750 --> 00:19:11,520
All right.

182
00:19:53,700 --> 00:19:55,869
   

183
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:02,210
Place it closer to the center.

184
00:20:03,310 --> 00:20:05,730
Put the fruits on the sides.

185
00:20:07,350 --> 00:20:09,140
Butler.

186
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:12,830
Mr. Zang.

187
00:20:12,830 --> 00:20:16,030
Are the offerings for the late marquis all prepared?

188
00:20:16,030 --> 00:20:20,810
Everything is ready. We're just waiting for the ceremony in the evening.

189
00:20:20,810 --> 00:20:22,790
Good. You can continue your work.

190
00:20:22,790 --> 00:20:24,520
Yes, sir.

191
00:21:28,070 --> 00:21:34,660
 Father, I know you made this incredible device not to kill people, 

192
00:21:34,660 --> 00:21:37,740
 but because you didn't want the technique lost. 

193
00:21:37,740 --> 00:21:40,880
 You cherished this skill deeply 

194
00:21:40,880 --> 00:21:44,450
 and never wanted it tainted by evil intent. 

195
00:21:44,450 --> 00:21:48,400
 But, Father, I have no choice now. 

196
00:21:48,400 --> 00:21:53,280
 It's in my hands, and I will use it to kill the Marquis of Pingjin, 

197
00:21:53,280 --> 00:21:57,680
 to avenge you, Mother, my younger sister, 

198
00:21:57,680 --> 00:22:00,960
 and all my fellow disciples! 

199
00:22:15,590 --> 00:22:17,450
Mr. Zang.

200
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:22,640
What are you doing?

201
00:22:22,640 --> 00:22:26,420
I was reconsidering the timing. Tonight's ceremony is at sunset.

202
00:22:26,420 --> 00:22:30,520
Sunset corresponds to wine vessels and symbolizes a good harvest.

203
00:22:30,520 --> 00:22:35,450
So, I moved the wine vessel to the left, to show respect.

204
00:22:40,350 --> 00:22:45,920
I got some ashes on it. I was just cleaning them.

205
00:22:48,200 --> 00:22:50,970
There's even a custom for this?

206
00:22:50,970 --> 00:22:54,240
You're truly meticulous, sir.

207
00:22:54,960 --> 00:22:56,730
It's my duty.

208
00:23:10,660 --> 00:23:12,643
   

209
00:23:18,000 --> 00:23:21,900
My Lord, it's time to light the incense.

210
00:23:36,600 --> 00:23:41,480
Father, everything at home is well.

211
00:23:41,480 --> 00:23:43,480
The Emperor still favors us greatly.

212
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:49,440
A few days ago, he praised Zhifu for his good work.

213
00:23:49,440 --> 00:23:53,110
You can rest easy in the afterlife.

214
00:23:53,110 --> 00:23:56,000
In a few days, on your death anniversary,

215
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:58,200
I'll take the family to the ancestral tombs

216
00:23:58,200 --> 00:24:02,430
to offer wine and burn incense in honor of our ancestors.

217
00:24:02,430 --> 00:24:04,380
I promise not to let you down.

218
00:24:04,380 --> 00:24:08,630
I'll preserve our legacy and ensure our family's future.

219
00:24:12,180 --> 00:24:16,140
   

220
00:24:38,270 --> 00:24:39,400
Father!

221
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:40,680
- Father! 
 - My Lord!

222
00:24:40,680 --> 00:24:41,880
- Father! 
 - My Lord!

223
00:24:41,880 --> 00:24:43,240
- My Lord! 
 - Father!

224
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:45,070
My Lord!

225
00:24:45,070 --> 00:24:47,680
- Father! 
 - My Lord!

226
00:24:47,680 --> 00:24:49,000
Father!

227
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:50,690
Father!

228
00:24:53,480 --> 00:24:55,440
Why isn't Zhixing here yet?

229
00:24:55,440 --> 00:24:57,920
My Lord, I've sent someone to find him.

230
00:24:57,920 --> 00:25:00,920
Zhixing hasn't been home since yesterday.

231
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:02,680
He probably went somewhere to play.

232
00:25:02,680 --> 00:25:04,400
 Why isn't the mechanism working? 

233
00:25:04,400 --> 00:25:07,740
When he returns, he'll answer for it.

234
00:25:09,110 --> 00:25:10,660
My Lord!

235
00:25:12,380 --> 00:25:17,470
My Lord, honoring ancestors is a serious family tradition.

236
00:25:18,880 --> 00:25:22,380
Perhaps we should wait for Second Young Master and do it together?

237
00:25:22,380 --> 00:25:24,240
Why wait for him?

238
00:25:24,240 --> 00:25:27,520
I don't want to see someone who has no respect for family tradition.

239
00:25:28,480 --> 00:25:31,570
Without him today, our numbers of people are off.

240
00:25:32,790 --> 00:25:35,650
The incense sticks in the burner aren't the lucky number nine.

241
00:25:35,650 --> 00:25:36,900
Nine returns to unity.

242
00:25:36,900 --> 00:25:41,070
I'm worried the late marquis might find it inauspicious in the afterlife.

243
00:25:41,070 --> 00:25:45,690
My father was fearless in battle, bold and free.

244
00:25:45,690 --> 00:25:48,000
He never believed in superstitions.

245
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:50,480
Even in the afterlife,

246
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:53,880
he wouldn't care about lucky numbers.

247
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:59,190
However, why are you so nervous?

248
00:26:01,110 --> 00:26:06,560
You've been staring at the burner since just now.

249
00:26:08,110 --> 00:26:10,430
Is something wrong?

250
00:26:10,430 --> 00:26:11,380
My Lord...

251
00:26:11,380 --> 00:26:12,940
My Lord,

252
00:26:13,940 --> 00:26:16,510
Mr. Zang always plans carefully.

253
00:26:16,510 --> 00:26:18,830
He just took care of arranging the ancestral hall

254
00:26:18,830 --> 00:26:21,460
and specially selected the incense.

255
00:26:26,640 --> 00:26:29,850
What's special about this incense?

256
00:26:33,480 --> 00:26:37,310
My Lord, these incenses were chosen by Mr. Zang.

257
00:26:37,310 --> 00:26:41,110
I noticed they are unusual.

258
00:26:41,110 --> 00:26:43,400
There's a golden thread inside each.

259
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:46,790
So, I took the liberty of replacing them.

260
00:26:46,790 --> 00:26:49,850
Mr. Zang, what is your intention here?

261
00:26:53,750 --> 00:26:55,350
Forgive me, My Lord.

262
00:26:55,350 --> 00:26:56,920
Today's ceremony honors the late marquis.

263
00:26:56,920 --> 00:26:59,210
These incenses contain golden threads.

264
00:26:59,210 --> 00:27:01,680
When burning the incense, fire melts gold,

