319
00:31:25,480 --> 00:31:28,510
My original plan was to flee in the chaos

320
00:31:28,510 --> 00:31:29,920
before the guards sealed off the mansion.

321
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:33,700
But unexpectedly, the steward swapped my incense.

322
