354
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:16,780
If you calm down now, you'll see it clearly.

355
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:21,880
The Marquis of Pingjin has many enemies.

356
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:25,000
Now you're his closest aide.

357
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:30,780
