If he dies, you're doomed, too.

361
00:33:41,850 --> 00:33:47,490
Killing the Marquis of Pingjin is the only reason I'm still alive.

362
00:34:06,640 --> 00:34:08,240
 Come in. 

363
00:34:17,710 --> 00:34:19,500
My Lord.

364
